SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Fract Excr from T1 to T2

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Fraction Bound
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The percent or ratio of bound substance concentration to the total concentration.
SKOS_CONCEPT.notation: Fraction Bound
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Fraction Bound

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Fraction of the Dose Metabolized
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The fraction of the bioavailable dose which has been metabolized.

SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Fraction of the Dose Metabolized

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Fraction Unbound
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The percent or ratio of free substance concentration to the total concentration. (NCI)
SKOS_CONCEPT.notation: Fraction Unbound
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Fraction Unbound

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Half Tmax
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The midpoint time between dosing time and Tmax.
SKOS_CONCEPT.notation: Half Tmax
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Half Tmax

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Half-Life Distribution
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: Half-life calculated from the distributional phase.
SKOS_CONCEPT.notation: Half-Life Distribution
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Half-Life Distribution

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Half-Life Lambda z
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: Terminal half-life.
SKOS_CONCEPT.notation: Half-Life Lambda z
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Terminal Half Life

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Half-Life TAU

SKOS_CONCEPT.notation: Half-Life TAU
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Half-Life TAU

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Hemodialysis Clearance
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The clearance of a substance from the blood during a hemodialysis session.

SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Hemodialysis Clearance

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Hemodialysis Extraction Ratio
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The fractional content of a substance removed from the blood during a hemodialysis session.

SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Hemodialysis Extraction Ratio

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Initial Conc Norm by BMI

SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Initial Concentration Normalized by Dose

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Initial Conc Norm by SA

SKOS_CONCEPT.notation: Initial Conc Norm by SA
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Initial Concentration Normalized by Surface Area

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Initial Conc Norm by WT
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: Initial concentration divided by the weight. Given only for bolus IV models.
SKOS_CONCEPT.notation: Initial Conc Norm by WT
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Initial Concentration Normalized by Weight

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Initial Conc
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: Initial concentration. Given only for bolus IV models.
SKOS_CONCEPT.notation: Initial Conc
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Initial Concentration

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: K Slope of Distribution

SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: K Slope of Distribution

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Lambda z Lower Limit TAU
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The lower limit on time for values to be included in the calculation of Lambda z, calculated within a dosing interval.
SKOS_CONCEPT.notation: Lambda z Lower Limit TAU
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Lambda z Lower Limit TAU

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Lambda z Lower Limit
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The lower limit on time for values to be included in the calculation of Lambda z.
SKOS_CONCEPT.notation: Lambda z Lower Limit
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Lambda Z Time Lower Limit

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Lambda z Span
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The interval of time covered by the data points used in the terminal disposition phase regression analysis, divided by half life. This yields the terminal disposition phase duration expressed as the number of half lives.
SKOS_CONCEPT.notation: Lambda z Span
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Lambda Z Span

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Lambda z TAU
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The first order rate constant associated with the terminal (log-linear) portion of the curve, calculated within a dosing interval.
SKOS_CONCEPT.notation: Lambda z TAU
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Lambda z TAU

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Lambda z Upper Limit TAU
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The upper limit on time for values to be included in the calculation of Lambda z, calculated within a dosing interval.
SKOS_CONCEPT.notation: Lambda z Upper Limit TAU
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Lambda z Upper Limit TAU

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Lambda z Upper Limit
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The upper limit on time for values to be included in the calculation of Lambda z.
SKOS_CONCEPT.notation: Lambda z Upper Limit
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Lambda Z Time Upper Limit

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Lambda z
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The first order rate constant associated with the terminal (log-linear) portion of the curve.
SKOS_CONCEPT.notation: Lambda z
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Lambda Z

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Last Meas Excretion Rate Norm by BMI
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The last measurable (positive) excretion rate divided by the body mass index.

SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Last Measurable Excretion Rate Normalized by Body Mass Index

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Last Meas Excretion Rate Norm by Dose
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The last measurable (positive) excretion rate divided by the dose.
SKOS_CONCEPT.notation: Last Meas Excretion Rate Norm by Dose
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Last Measurable Excretion Rate Normalized by Dose

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Last Meas Excretion Rate Norm by SA
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The last measurable (positive) excretion rate divided by the surface area.
SKOS_CONCEPT.notation: Last Meas Excretion Rate Norm by SA
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Last Measurable Excretion Rate Normalized by Surface Area

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Last Meas Excretion Rate Norm by WT
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The last measurable (positive) excretion rate divided by the weight.
SKOS_CONCEPT.notation: Last Meas Excretion Rate Norm by WT
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Last Measurable Excretion Rate Normalized by Weight

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Last Meas Excretion Rate
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The last measurable (positive) excretion rate determined for the specimen type specified in PPSPEC.
SKOS_CONCEPT.notation: Last Meas Excretion Rate
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Last Measurable Observed Excretion Rate

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Last Nonzero Conc Norm by BMI
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The concentration corresponding to Tlast divided by the body mass index.
SKOS_CONCEPT.notation: Last Nonzero Conc Norm by BMI
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Last Concentration Normalized by Body Mass Index

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Last Nonzero Conc Norm by Dose
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The concentration corresponding to Tlast divided by the dose.
SKOS_CONCEPT.notation: Last Nonzero Conc Norm by Dose
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Last Concentration Normalized by Dose

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Last Nonzero Conc Norm by SA
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The concentration corresponding to Tlast divided by the surface area.

SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Last Concentration Normalized by Surface Area

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Last Nonzero Conc Norm by WT
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The concentration corresponding to Tlast divided by the weight.

SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Last Concentration Normalized by Weight

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Last Nonzero Conc
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The concentration corresponding to Tlast.
SKOS_CONCEPT.notation: Last Nonzero Conc
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Last Concentration

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Max Conc LN Transformed
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The natural log transformed maximum concentration occurring at Tmax.

SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Natural Log Transformed Cmax

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Max Conc Norm by BMI
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The maximum concentration occurring at Tmax, divided by the body mass index.
SKOS_CONCEPT.notation: Max Conc Norm by BMI
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Maximum Concentration Normalized by Body Mass Index

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Max Conc Norm by Dose
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The maximum concentration occurring at Tmax, divided by the dose.
SKOS_CONCEPT.notation: Max Conc Norm by Dose
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Maximum Concentration Dose Normalized

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Max Conc Norm by Dose/WT
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The maximum concentration occurring at Tmax divided by the body weight-adjusted dose.
SKOS_CONCEPT.notation: Max Conc Norm by Dose/WT
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Maximum Concentration Normalized by Weight-Adjusted Dose

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Max Conc Norm by SA
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The maximum concentration occurring at Tmax, divided by the surface area.
SKOS_CONCEPT.notation: Max Conc Norm by SA
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Maximum Concentration Normalized by Surface Area

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Max Conc Norm by WT
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The maximum concentration occurring at Tmax, divided by the weight.

SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Maximum Concentration Normalized by Weight

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Max Conc, Unbound Drug
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The maximum concentration represented by the unbound fraction of drug, occurring at Tmax.

SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Maximum Concentration of Unbound Drug

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Max Excretion Rate Norm by BMI
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The maximum excretion rate divided by the body mass index.
SKOS_CONCEPT.notation: Max Excretion Rate Norm by BMI
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Maximum Observed Excretion Rate Normalized by Body Mass Index

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Max Excretion Rate Norm by Dose
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The maximum excretion rate divided by the dose.
SKOS_CONCEPT.notation: Max Excretion Rate Norm by Dose
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Maximum Observed Excretion Rate Normalized by Dose

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Max Excretion Rate Norm by SA
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The maximum excretion rate divided by the surface area.
SKOS_CONCEPT.notation: Max Excretion Rate Norm by SA
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Maximum Observed Excretion Rate Normalized by Surface Area

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Max Excretion Rate Norm by WT
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The maximum excretion rate divided by the weight.
SKOS_CONCEPT.notation: Max Excretion Rate Norm by WT
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Maximum Observed Excretion Rate Normalized by Weight

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Max Excretion Rate
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The maximum excretion rate determined for the specimen type specified in PPSPEC.
SKOS_CONCEPT.notation: Max Excretion Rate
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Maximum Observed Excretion Rate

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Mean Absorption Time
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: Mean absorption time of a substance administered by extravascular dosing.
SKOS_CONCEPT.notation: Mean Absorption Time
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Mean Absorption Time

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Midpoint of Interval of Last Nonzero ER
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The midpoint of collection interval associated with last measurable excretion rate.
SKOS_CONCEPT.notation: Midpoint of Interval of Last Nonzero ER
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Collection Interval Midpoint

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Midpoint of Interval of Maximum ER
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The midpoint of collection interval associated with the maximum excretion rate.
SKOS_CONCEPT.notation: Midpoint of Interval of Maximum ER
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Time of Maximum Observed Excretion Rate

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Min Conc Norm by BMI
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The minimum concentration between dose time and dose time plus Tau (at Tmin) divided by the body mass index.
SKOS_CONCEPT.notation: Min Conc Norm by BMI
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Minimum Concentration Normalized by Body Mass Index

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Min Conc Norm by Dose
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The minimum concentration between dose time and dose time plus Tau (at Tmin) divided by the dose.
SKOS_CONCEPT.notation: Min Conc Norm by Dose
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Minimum Concentration Normalized by Dose

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Min Conc Norm by Dose/WT
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The minimum concentration between dose time and dose time plus Tau (at Tmin) divided by the body weight-adjusted dose.

SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Minimum Concentration Normalized by Surface Area

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Min Conc Norm by WT
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The minimum concentration between dose time and dose time plus Tau (at Tmin) divided by the weight.
SKOS_CONCEPT.notation: Min Conc Norm by WT
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Minimum Concentration Normalized by Weight

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Min Conc
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The minimum concentration between dose time and dose time plus Tau (at Tmin).
SKOS_CONCEPT.notation: Min Conc
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Cmin

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: MRT Extravasc Infinity Obs
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The mean residence time (MRT) extrapolated to infinity for a substance administered by extravascular dosing, calculated using the observed value of the last non-zero concentration. Extravascular MRT includes Mean Absorption Time (MAT).
SKOS_CONCEPT.notation: MRT Extravasc Infinity Obs
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Mean Residence Time Infinity Observed by Extravascular Dose

SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The mean residence time (MRT) extrapolated to infinity for a substance administered by extravascular dosing, calculated using the predicted value of the last non-zero concentration. Extravascular MRT includes Mean Absorption Time (MAT).
SKOS_CONCEPT.notation: MRT Extravasc Infinity Pred
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Mean Residence Time Infinity Predicted by Extravascular Dose

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: MRT Extravasc to Last Nonzero Conc

SKOS_CONCEPT.notation: MRT Extravasc to Last Nonzero Conc
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Mean Residence Time to Last Nonzero Concentration by Extravascular Dose

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: MRT IV Bolus Infinity Obs

SKOS_CONCEPT.notation: MRT IV Bolus Infinity Obs
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Mean Residence Time Infinity Observed by Intravascular Bolus Dose

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: MRT IV Bolus Infinity Pred
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The mean residence time (MRT) extrapolated to infinity for a substance administered by intravascular bolus dosing, calculated using the predicted value of the last non-zero concentration.
SKOS_CONCEPT.notation: MRT IV Bolus Infinity Pred
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Mean Residence Time Infinity Predicted by Intravascular Bolus Dose

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: MRT IV Bolus to Last Nonzero Conc

SKOS_CONCEPT.notation: MRT IV Bolus to Last Nonzero Conc
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Mean Residence Time to Last Nonzero Concentration by Intravascular Bolus Dose

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: MRT IV Cont Inf Infinity Obs
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The mean residence time (MRT) extrapolated to infinity for a substance administered by constant rate of continuous intravascular infusion, calculated using the observed value of the last non-zero concentration.
SKOS_CONCEPT.notation: MRT IV Cont Inf Infinity Obs
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Mean Residence Time Intravenous Continuous Infusion Infinity Observed

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: MRT IV Cont Inf Infinity Pred
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The mean residence time (MRT) extrapolated to infinity for a substance administered by constant rate of continuous intravascular infusion, calculated using the predicted value of the last non-zero concentration.
SKOS_CONCEPT.notation: MRT IV Cont Inf Infinity Pred
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Mean Residence Time Intravenous Continuous Infusion Infinity Predicted

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: MRT IV Cont Inf to Last Nonzero Conc
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: Mean residence time (MRT) from the time of dosing to the time of the last measurable concentration, for a substance administered by constant rate of continuous intravascular infusion.

SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Mean Residence Time Intravenous Continuous Infusion to Last Nonzero Concentration

SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Nonrenal Clearance Normalized by SA

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Nonrenal CL Norm by WT
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The total clearance of a substance from the blood minus the renal clearance divided by the weight.
SKOS_CONCEPT.notation: Nonrenal CL Norm by WT
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Nonrenal Clearance Normalized by WT

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Nonrenal CL
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The total clearance of a substance from the blood less the renal clearance.
SKOS_CONCEPT.notation: Nonrenal CL
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Nonrenal Clearance

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Number of Points for Lambda z TAU
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The number of time points used in computing Lambda z determined in a dosing interval.
SKOS_CONCEPT.notation: Number of Points for Lambda z TAU
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Number of Points for Lambda z TAU

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Number of Points for Lambda z
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The number of time points used in computing Lambda z.
SKOS_CONCEPT.notation: Number of Points for Lambda z
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Sum of Lambda Z Timepoints

SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The percentage of the administered dose that is recovered from the specimen type specified in PPSPEC, over the interval between T1 and T2.
SKOS_CONCEPT.notation: Pct Rec from T1 to T2
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Percent Recovered from T1 to T2

SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The percentage of the administered dose that is recovered from the specimen type specified in PPSPEC extrapolated to infinity, calculated using the observed value of the last non-zero concentration, divided by the body mass index.

SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Percent Recovered Infinity Observed Normalized by Body Mass Index

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Pct Rec Infinity Obs Norm by SA
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The percentage of the administered dose that is recovered from the specimen type specified in PPSPEC extrapolated to infinity, calculated using the observed value of the last non-zero concentration, divided by the surface area.

SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Percent Recovered Infinity Observed Normalized by Weight

SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Percent Recovered Infinity Predicted Normalized by Body Mass Index

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Pct Rec Infinity Pred Norm by SA

SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Percent Recovered Infinity Predicted Normalized by Surface Area

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Pct Rec Infinity Pred Norm by WT

SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Percent Recovered Infinity Predicted Normalized by Weight

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Pct Rec Infinity Pred

SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Percent Recovered Infinity Predicted

SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Percent Recovered Over Dosing Interval Normalized by Body Mass Index

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Pct Rec Over Dosing Interval Norm by SA
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The percentage of the administered dose that is recovered from the specimen type specified in PPSPEC, between doses (TAU) divided by surface area.
SKOS_CONCEPT.notation: Pct Rec Over Dosing Interval Norm by SA
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Percent Recovered Over Dosing Interval Normalized by Surface Area

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Pct Rec Over Dosing Interval Norm by WT
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The percentage of the administered dose that is recovered from the specimen type specified in PPSPEC, between doses (TAU) divided by weight.

SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Percent Recovered Over Dosing Interval

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Ratio Conc Trough

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Ratio Min Conc
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The ratio of two cmin values.
SKOS_CONCEPT.notation: Ratio Min Conc

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Ratio of CMAX to CMIN
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The ratio of Cmax value to Cmin value.

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Ratio AUC to Last Nonzero Conc Norm by Dose

SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Ratio AUC to Last Nonzero Concentration Normalized by Dose

SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Relative Bioavailability

SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Renal Clearance to Total Clearance Ratio Measurement After Oral Dosing

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Renal CL as Pct CL IV
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The portion of total clearance attributed to the kidneys expressed as a percentage, following intravenous administration.
SKOS_CONCEPT.notation: Renal CL as Pct CL IV
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Renal Clearance to Total Clearance Ratio Measurement After Intravenous Dosing

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Renal CL for Dose Int Norm by BMI
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The clearance of a substance from the blood by the kidneys, calculated using AUCTAU, divided by the body mass index.
SKOS_CONCEPT.notation: Renal CL for Dose Int Norm by BMI
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Renal Clearance for Dose Interval Normalized by Body Mass Index

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Renal CL for Dose Int Norm by Dose

SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Renal Clearance for Dose Interval Normalized by Dose

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Renal CL for Dose Int Norm by SA

SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Renal Clearance for Dose Interval Normalized by Surface Area

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Renal CL for Dose Int Norm by WT

SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Renal Clearance for Dose Interval Normalized by Weight

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Renal CL for Dose Int

SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Renal Clearance for Dose Interval

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Renal CL from T1 to T2 Norm by BMI

SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Renal Clearance from T1 to T2 Normalized by Body Mass Index

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Renal CL from T1 to T2 Norm by Dose
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The clearance of a substance from the blood by the kidneys over the interval from T1 to T2 divided by the dose.

SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Renal Clearance from T1 to T2 Normalized by Dose

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Renal CL from T1 to T2 Norm by SA
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The clearance of a substance from the blood by the kidneys over the interval from T1 to T2 divided by the surface area.

SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Renal Clearance from T1 to T2 Normalized by Surface Area

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Renal CL from T1 to T2 Norm by WT

SKOS_CONCEPT.notation: Renal CL from T1 to T2 Norm by WT
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Renal Clearance from T1 to T2 Normalized by Weight

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Renal CL from T1 to T2
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The clearance of a substance from the blood by the kidneys over the interval from T1 to T2.
SKOS_CONCEPT.notation: Renal CL from T1 to T2
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Renal Clearance from T1 to T2

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Renal CL Norm by BMI
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The clearance of a substance from the blood by the kidneys divided by the body mass index.
SKOS_CONCEPT.notation: Renal CL Norm by BMI
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Renal Clearance Normalized by BMI

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Renal CL Norm by Dose
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The clearance of a substance from the blood by the kidneys divided by the dose.

SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Renal Clearance Normalized by Dose

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Renal CL Norm by SA

SKOS_CONCEPT.notation: Renal CL Norm by SA
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Renal Clearance Normalized by SA

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Renal CL Norm by WT

SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Renal Clearance Normalized by WT

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Renal CL
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The clearance of a substance from the blood by the kidneys.
SKOS_CONCEPT.notation: Renal CL
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Renal Clearance

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Stationarity Ratio AUC
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The area under the curve (AUCTAU) at steady state divided by the area under the curve extrapolated to infinity for the initial dosing interval.
SKOS_CONCEPT.notation: Stationarity Ratio AUC
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Stationarity Ratio Area Under the Curve

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Sum of Urine Vol
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The sum of urine volumes that are used for PK parameters.

SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Sum Urine Volume

SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: PK Swing

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Time of CMAX

SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Tmax

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Time of CMIN Observation
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The time of minimum concentration sampled during a dosing interval.
SKOS_CONCEPT.notation: Time of CMIN Observation
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Tmin

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Time of Last Nonzero Conc
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The time of the last measurable (positive) concentration.
SKOS_CONCEPT.notation: Time of Last Nonzero Conc
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Time of Last Nonzero Concentration

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Time Until First Nonzero Conc
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The time prior to the first measurable (non-zero) concentration.

SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Time until First Nonzero Concentration

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Total CL by F for Dose Int Norm by BMI
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The total body clearance for extravascular administration divided by the fraction of dose absorbed, calculated using AUCTAU, divided by the body mass index.
SKOS_CONCEPT.notation: Total CL by F for Dose Int Norm by BMI
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Total Body Clearance by Fraction of Dose for Dose Interval Normalized by Body Mass Index

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Total CL by F for Dose Int Norm by Dose
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The total body clearance for extravascular administration divided by the fraction of dose absorbed, calculated using AUCTAU, divided by the dose.

SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Total Body Clearance by Fraction of Dose for Dose Interval Normalized by Dose

SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Total Body Clearance for Dose Interval Normalized by Body Mass Index

SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The total body clearance for intravascular administration, calculated using AUCTAU, divided by the dose.

SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Total Body Clearance for Dose Interval Normalized by Dose

SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Total Body Clearance for Dose Interval Normalized by Weight

SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Total Body Clearance for Dose Interval

SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Total Clearance Observed by Fraction Dose Normalized by Dose

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Total CL Obs by F Norm by SA

SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The total body clearance for intravascular administration, calculated using the observed value of the last non-zero concentration, divided by the body mass index.

SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Total Clearance Observed Normalized by Weight

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Total CL Pred Norm by Dose

SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Total Clearance Predicted Normalized by Dose

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Total CL Pred Norm by SA
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The total body clearance for intravascular administration, calculated using the predicted value of the last non-zero concentration, divided by the surface area.
SKOS_CONCEPT.notation: Total CL Pred Norm by SA
SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Total Clearance Predicted Normalized by Surface Area

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Total CL Pred Norm by WT
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: The total body clearance for intravascular administration, calculated using the predicted value of the last non-zero concentration, divided by the weight.

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: Total CL Pred

SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Observed Steady State Volume of Distribution Normalized by Body Mass Index

SKOS_CONCEPT.pref_label: Observed Steady State Volume of Distribution Normalized by Dose
